blueprint.description:
Only 1/2 a block.
Requires Waterfill or Pump Anywhere.
Manual construction.
Can be filled in as needed.
Inserters are "burner" and will feed themselves ahead of boilers so work even in brown-out situations.
Can be updated to electric inserters and be powered separately if necessary (e.g. to recover from a complete blackout).
